    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_320065",
        "quote": "Thought is constantly creating problems that way and then trying to solve them. But as it tries to solve them it makes it worse because it doesn't notice that it's creating them, and the more it thinks, the more problems it creates.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David Bohm",
            "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_320065"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Thought",
                "url": "/topics/thought"
