            {
                "name": "Engaged",
                "url": "/topics/engaged"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_320069",
        "quote": "What is the source of all this trouble? I'm saying that the source is basically in thought. Many people would think that such a statement is crazy, because thought is the one thing we have with which to solve our problems. That's part of our tradition.",
