            "name": "David Bohm",
            "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_130977"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Self-Deception",
                "url": "/topics/self-deception"
            },
            {
                "name": "Constitute",
                "url": "/topics/constitute"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_321088",
        "quote": "In relativity, movement is continuous, causally determinate and well defined, while in quantum mechanics it is discontinuous, not causally determinate and not well defined.",
