            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_320050",
        "quote": "But you don't decide what to do with the info. Thought runs you. Thought, however, gives false info that you are running it, that you are the one who controls thought. Whereas actually thought is the one which controls each one of us.",
