                "url": "/topics/keeping"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_320054",
        "quote": "Indeed, the attempt to live according to the notion that the fragments are really separate is, in essence, what has led to the growing series of extremely urgent crises that is confronting us today.",
