                "url": "/topics/proper"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_320056",
        "quote": "People are no longer primarily in opposition, nor can they be said to be interacting, rather they are participating in this pool of common meaning which is capable of constant development and change.",
