                "name": "Constant",
                "url": "/topics/constant"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_320058",
        "quote": "So one begins to wonder what is going to happen to the human race. Technology keeps on advancing with greater and greater power, either for good or for destruction.",
