                "url": "/topics/actual"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_bohm_320062",
        "quote": "This is another major feature of thought: Thought doesn't know it is doing something and then it struggles against it is doing. It doesn't want to know that it is doing it.",
